ers<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Color: Black, professional paint with primer standard<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Plug: 7-way RV connector<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Stake Pockets: Along both sides<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Why Choose the Big Tex 10LX?<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>This model combines strength, versatility, and premium construction\\u2014ideal for hauling gravel, debris, equipment, manure, and other materials. With its powerful hydraulic dump system and reinforced steel build, the 10LX is a reliable workhorse that performs day after day.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Available Now at Varner Equipment<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Price: $8,560<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span>Stock #100453<\\/span><\\/p>\\n\",\"seller_info\":\"<p>Call or stop by to see it in person<\\/p>\\n<p>Varner Equipment<\\/p>\\n<p>1375 Hwy 50<\\/p>\\n<p>Delta, CO 81416<\\/p>\\n<p>(970) 874-0612<\\/p>\\n\",\"featured\":false,\"show_on_website\":true,\"images\":[\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP-1.webp\",\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP2-1.webp\",\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP4-1.webp\",\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP6-1.webp\",\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP7-1.webp\",\"https:\\/\\/varnerequipdev.wpenginepowered.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2026\\/05\\/14LP8-1.webp\"],\"image_ids\":[592,596,597,595,594,593],\"implements\":[],\"deleted_at\":\"\",\"last_action\":\"create\",\"last_actor_name\":\"varnerequipdev\",\"last_actor_initials\":\"V\",\"last_action_at\":\"2026-05-04 21:53:17\"}}',NULL,'2026-05-05 18:22:14');
